      "content": "Right, I get that the system is biased, but from a purely data-driven perspective, how much of that is actually attributable to socioeconomic factors versus inherent behavioral trends within those specific communities? I'm trying to differentiate between systemic policing bias and actual crime frequency in those demographics for my analysis.",
